style: none; background-color: #ffffff; border-color: #000000;">
<tbody>
<tr style=3D"height: 26px;">
<td style=3D"width: 33.3333%; height: 26px;"></td>
<td style=3D"width: 34.0492%; height: 26px; text-align: center;"><span styl=
e=3D"color: #ff9900;"><strong>Advantages</strong></span></td>
<td style=3D"width: 32.6174%; height: 26px; text-align: center;"><span styl=
e=3D"color: #ff9900;"><strong>Disadvantages</strong></span></td>
</tr>
<tr style=3D"height: 54px; border-color: #000000;">
<td style=3D"width: 33.3333%; height: 54px;"><strong><span style=3D"color: =
#000080;">Decrease the RF power level</span></strong></td>
<td style=3D"width: 34.0492%; height: 54px; text-align: center;">A simple w=
ay to preserve battery, if the read range does not represent an issue</td>
<td style=3D"width: 32.6174%; height: 54px; text-align: center;">Not effici=
ent in term of power savings</td>
</tr>
<tr style=3D"height: 26px;">
<td style=3D"width: 33.3333%; height: 11px;"><strong><span style=3D"color: =
#000080;">Use an RF off time parameter in continue scanning mode</span></st=
rong></td>
<td style=3D"width: 34.0492%; height: 11px; text-align: center;">Decreases =
the energy consumption without affecting the reading distance</td>
<td style=3D"width: 32.6174%; height: 11px; text-align: center;">The reacti=
ve ability in reading is reduced</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style=3D"width: 33.3333%;"><strong><span style=3D"color: #000080;">&nbs=
p;</span></strong></td>
